{{G|Europe occidentale|45.76|4.84|Lyon|Ville|3|w}}
{{G|Europe occidentale|43.677|4.628|Arles|Ville|3|s}}
{{G|Europe occidentale|45.46|9.19|Milan|Ville|3|s}}
{{G|Europe occidentale|44.417|12.2|Ravenne|Ville|3|e}}
